The most beautiful thing about getting older is having a chance to be reunited with people who made a huge impact on your life years later….and getting to hug them, and thank them, and truly appreciate the small moments in the journey of this darn tootin” life. 

This is @paradepicturesworldwide (David Warry-Smith). We recently got to work together and did that “What did we work on together???” Thing. 

WELLLLLLLLLL - David gave me my VERY FIRST ACTING JOB!  On a long forgotten show called Two that he was directing.  I was originally auditioning for a smaller role, and after I read David said he wanted me to go out in the hall for 20 min and learn the sides for the guest star. (This was like a super big deal for me at the time). 

I got the part. I’ll never forget calling my parents and screaming into the phone I GOT THE PART!!!!!! Which remains a long running joke between me and my parents. 

Getting this part completely changed the course of my life and my career. Getting to see David and tell him that story….and how what was likely an insignificant moment in his life had a massive impact on mine was honestly such a perfect full circle moment for me. We don’t always get that chance . Forever and ever beyond grateful. . THANK YOU DAVID!!!!!!!!!

I struggle big time w fun rest day ideas - I have a hard time finding that chill zone. 

Got inspired by a friend to use my sliders and forgot how much fun it is! Don’t have sliders? Just use two towels! (I used two pillows at one point cause it hurt my knees 😆) 

Went on YouTube and did the ol’ search and so many workouts were available. This was from @redefiningstrength 

A great zero impact core and stability session that anyone can do w a couple towels and a non carpeted surface. So no excuses! 

#training #restday #restdaydoesntmeansitonthesofa #core #stability #sliders #basementworkout

I know we talk about how much representation matters, and how important it is for all of us to look at the screen and see ourselves represented. I feel it’s important that we also get a chance to understand other peoples lives, their perspective, through their own lived experiences. 

@seantowgood is freakin’ brilliant - he’s been underestimated, judged, overlooked and not seen - by so many people - for far too many years. I am so happy that the world….er well Canada is going to get to meet this wickedly hilarious human who is so talented, so smart and so driven and unwilling to give up on his dreams no matter how many times he’s been knocked down. Sean created, wrote, produced and is starring in this show!!!!! Never ever underestimate any person. EVER! Sean I hope all your haters are watching!!!! Shine baby Shine!!!!

#YoureMyHero #TELUSfund

Then the universe was like…. “that’s super great that that’s what YOU want….but I’m the universe and I decide what you need.” Anyway turns out I needed these cute sunglasses, lots of different lakes, time with my kids and husband and time with close friends. Can’t fight the universe. Just gotta go with the flow baby!! I’m not angry about it at all.
